{"tid":765271,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"一個人睇戲真係好爽","createTime":"2018-08-02T15:31:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T02:19:58.000Z","uid":71508,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f9ea91cd589dae06d893d3913b795f61704aec6b","tid":765271,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T15:31:08.000Z","msg":"岩先晏就無野做，走去睇超人特工隊2<br />\n見到大院，L排，岩岩好有個單丁位係一流 <br />\n可以留一格係左右隔開其他人 <br />\n過兩格個位就會變左斜視位，無咩人會肯買 <br />\n又有左右扶手任放對手 <br />\n附近又可以無咩人 <br />\n雖然個場無咩人 <br />\n但都唔洗諗，光速買飛 <br />\n<br />\n入到場， <br />\n見到同我同一排有個女仔都係單丁睇戲 <br />\n估唔到都係識貨之人 <br />\n不過一睇就知個女仔係新手 <br />\n個位隔黎連住兩個唔識既男仔 <br />\n可惜，真係可惜， <br />\n下次有機會見到戰友真係要搭訕交流下心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c430952a90a418f0bf4ca195e100102b80185f3","tid":765271,"uid":132587,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T15:44:46.000Z","msg":"最後兩句好尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e3a85930dc289a47eaa946c797f9eb339c74869","tid":765271,"uid":185670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T15:46:58.000Z","msg":"我係咪同你同場 我又係自己睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3f7423a0c7a8b6a4d765e7940a2ad6b50cd2d95","tid":765271,"uid":99568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T15:47:23.000Z","msg":"Ching <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02c84522492eee633314f69cf90a2eceb1106eaf","tid":765271,"uid":9430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T15:50:52.000Z","msg":"巴打有咩心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪一開賣就捕住counter有無靚女買單丁位"},{"pid":"fa010ecfaa66a5bae6a45c47b42b46abc5fbf6e8","tid":765271,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3f7423a0c7a8b6a4d765e7940a2ad6b50cd2d95","tid":765271,"uid":99568,"like":1,"di